{"title":"最小生成树","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":256,"tags":["模板"],"operation":{"submit":"https://syzoj.com/problem/447#submit_code","submissions":"https://syzoj.com/submissions?problem_id=447","statistics":"https://syzoj.com/problem/447/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://syzoj.com/problem/447/testdata","discussion":"https://syzoj.com/discussion/problem/447"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"给定结点数为 $n$，边数为 $m$ 的带权无向连通图 $G$，所有结点编号为 $1,2,\\cdots,n$。\r\n\r\n求 $G$ 的最小生成树的边权和。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行两个正整数 $n,m$。\r\n\r\n之后的 $m$ 行，每行三个正整数 $u_i,v_i,w_i$（$1\\le u_i,v_i\\le n$，$0\\le w_i\\le 10^9$），描述一条连接结点 $u_i$ 和 $v_i$，边权为 $w_i$ 的边。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"一个整数表示 $G$ 的最小生成树的边权和。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"#### 样例输入\r\n```plain\r\n7 12\r\n1 2 9\r\n1 5 2\r\n1 6 3\r\n2 3 5\r\n2 6 7\r\n3 4 6\r\n3 7 3\r\n4 5 6\r\n4 7 2\r\n5 6 3\r\n5 7 6\r\n6 7 1\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出\r\n```plain\r\n16\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$1\\le n\\le 2\\times 10^5$，$0\\le m\\le 5\\times 10^5$。"}]}